transmitter

  BNO
  sda to a4 
  scl to a5
  vcc to 5v
  gnd to gnd

  flex
  terminal 1 as a pulldown 
  terminal 2 to gnd

  voltage divider
  5v--10k resistor--analog input tapped out--flex--gnd

  push button is connected to d2 and gnd(on click it gives a digital signal to the nano )
  
  
  HC-05
  vcc--hc-05's(5v)
  gnd--hc-05's(gnd)
  d10--tx
  d11--rx
receiver 
  vcc--hc-05's(5v)
  gnd--hc-05's(gnd)
  d10--tx
  d11--rx
  
